{{Infobox language |name=Duli |nativename=Duli-Gewe |region=northern [[Cameroon]] |extinct=? |ref=e13<!--Duli "nearly extinct", Gey extinct, in e12--> |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Leko–Nimbari languages|Leko–Nimbari]] |fam4=[[Duru languages|Duru]] |fam5= |iso3=duz |glotto=duli1241 |glottorefname=Duli }}
