{{Infobox language
|name       = Middle High German
|nativename = ''{{lang|gmh|Diutsch}}''
|region     = Central and southern [[Germany]] (south of the [[Benrath line]]), [[Austria]] and parts of [[Switzerland]]
|era        = [[High Middle Ages]]
|familycolor= Indo-European
