==== Possessive pronouns ====
The possessive pronouns ''{{lang|gmh|mîn, dîn, sîn, ir, unser, iuwer}}'' are used like adjectives and hence take on adjective endings following the normal rules. This includes ''{{lang|gmh|unser}}'' and ''{{lang|gmh|iuwer}}'', despite the fact that they already end in ''{{lang|gmh|-er}}''.

